title: Global annual catch of tuna, tuna-like and shark species (%year_start%-%year_end%) (IRD level 0)
description:
This dataset lists global catch of tuna and tuna-like species from %year_start% to %year_end%. Catches are stratified by year, species, fishing gear, vessel flag reporting country, area (essentially the tuna RFMOs areas of management). This dataset was computed using public domain catch-and-effort datasets released by the five tuna Regional Fisheries Management Organizations: the Indian Ocean Tuna Commission (IOTC), the International Commission for the Conservation of Atlantic Tunas (ICCAT), the Inter-American Tropical Tuna Commission (IATTC), The Western and Central Pacific Fisheries Commission (WCPFC), the Commission for the Conservation of Southern Bluefin Tuna (CCSBT). 

IRD Level 0 stands for the processes applied to the primary datasets by the French National Research Institute for Sustainable Development (IRD) to generate the dataset.
